\par \tab He watched Novi\rquote s eyes glisten and was pleased that they did.
\par \tab She said, \ldblquote I try hard to learn all you teach me, Master.\rdblquote 
\par \tab \ldblquote I\rquote m sure you will,\rdblquote  he said\endash and then hesitated. It occurred to him that, in his conversation with Compor, he had in no way indicated at any time that he was not alone. There was no hint of a companion.
\par \tab A woman could be taken for granted, perhaps; at least, Compor would no doubt not be surprised.\endash But a Hamishwoman?
\par \tab For a moment, despite anything Gendibal could do, the stereotype reigned supreme and he found himself glad that Compor had never been on Trantor and would not recognize Novi as a Hamishwoman.
