Still, the Sirius Sector does have a long history, so every world in it should be well known and it should be easy to check the matter, even without going there.\rdblquote 
\par \tab Pelorat chuckled. \ldblquote Even if you were to show that no world in the Sirius Sector could possibly be Earth, that wouldn\rquote t help. You underestimate the depths to which mysticism can bury rationality, Golan. 
