have disappeared in his concern for Sura Novi. He needed no mentalics to see that stepping into nothingness had totally upset her.
\par \tab \ldblquote I be afeared, Master,\rdblquote  she said when he explained what would have to be done. \ldblquote It be naughtness into which I will make footstep.\rdblquote 
 If nothing else, her sudden descent into thick Hamish dialect showed the extent of her disturbance.
\par \tab Gendibal said gently, \ldblquote I cannot leave you on board this ship, Novi, for I will be going into the other and I must have you with me. There is no dang
er, for your space suit will protect you from all harm and there is no place for you to fall to. Even if you lose your grip on the tether, you will remain nearly where you are and I will be within arm\rquote 
s reach so that I can gather you in. Come, Novi, show me that you are brave enough\endash as well as bright enough\endash to become a scholar.\rdblquote 
\par \tab She made no further objection and Gendibal, unwilling to do anything that might disturb the smoothness of her mind-set, nevertheless managed to inject a soothing touch upon the surface of her mind.
