\par \tab \ldblquote And then can we be taken to whoever it is that you speak of as Gaia?\rdblquote  said Trevize.
\par \tab Bliss looked amused. \ldblquote I don\rquote t know if you\rquote re going to believe this, Trev. I\rquote m Gaia.\rdblquote 
