\par \tab Pelorat laughed. \ldblquote I wouldn\rquote t count on much boyish ardor, Bliss, but if I had it I could do worse than have it on your account, I think.\rdblquote 
\par \tab Bliss said, \ldblquote Oh, don\rquote t discount your boyish ardor. I work wonders.\rdblquote 
