\par \tab Bliss, who was looking straight ahead, said calmly, \ldblquote I know, Trev, that you have suspected that I/we/Gaia was interested in you.\rdblquote 
\par \tab \ldblquote \lquote I/we/Gaia\rquote ?\rdblquote  said Pelorat softly.
