\par \tab STOR GENDEBAL WAS EDGING TOWARD GAIA ALMOST AS CAUTIOUSLY AS Trevize had\endash and now that its star was a perceptible disc and could be viewed only through strong filters, he paused to consider.
\par \tab Sura Novi sat to one side, looking up at him now and then in a timorous manner.
\par \tab She said softly, \ldblquote Master?\rdblquote 
